    const-string p1, "\n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>1.How can I withdraw cash?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>There are cash rewards for each level you pass. The more levels you pass, the more rewards you get. You can withdraw cash when you meet the requirements.</font><br>\n<br>\n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>2.How long does it take to withdraw money?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>Generally, the funds will be credited to your account within a few minutes. When the number of withdrawals or the amount exceeds a certain limit, the system will review it, but it will also be credited to your account within 24 hours, please don\'t worry.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>3.Why did my withdrawal fail?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>If the withdrawal fails, the system will feedback the reason for the failure (in English). Please modify it according to the prompts. If the withdrawal fails, the system will return the withdrawal amount. You can modify your withdrawal information and re-initiate the withdrawal.\nPlease make sure the information you fill in is correct. We are not responsible for any withdrawal failure caused by incorrect information.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>4.How many times can I withdraw?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>Unlimited.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>5.How many times can I withdraw a day?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>5times/day.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>6.Why can\'t I withdraw funds using my withdrawal account?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>The same withdrawal account can only be bound to two app accounts at most. Please do not share account with others.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>7.Can I use VPN?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>The use of VPN is prohibited, please do not use it.</font><br>"

    .line 7
    .line 8
    iput-object p1, p0, Lw3/j;->c:Ljava/lang/String;

    .line 9
    .line 10
    const-string p1, "\n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>1.Como posso sacar dinheiro?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>H\u00e1 recompensas em dinheiro para cada n\u00edvel que voc\u00ea passar. Quanto mais n\u00edveis voc\u00ea passar, mais recompensas receber\u00e1. Voc\u00ea pode sacar dinheiro quando cumprir os requisitos.</font><br>\n<br>\n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>2.Quanto tempo demora para sacar dinheiro?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>Geralmente, os fundos ser\u00e3o creditados em sua conta em poucos minutos. Quando o n\u00famero de saques ou o valor ultrapassar um determinado limite, o sistema analisar\u00e1 o valor, mas tamb\u00e9m ser\u00e1 creditado em sua conta em at\u00e9 24 horas. N\u00e3o se preocupe.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>3.Por que minha retirada falhou?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>Se o saque falhar, o sistema retornar\u00e1 o motivo da falha (em ingl\u00eas). Modifique-o de acordo com as instru\u00e7\u00f5es. Se o saque falhar, o sistema retornar\u00e1 o valor do saque. Voc\u00ea pode modificar suas informa\u00e7\u00f5es de saque e reinici\u00e1-lo.\nCertifique-se de que as informa\u00e7\u00f5es preenchidas estejam corretas. N\u00e3o nos responsabilizamos por qualquer falha no saque causada por informa\u00e7\u00f5es incorretas.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>4.Quantas vezes posso sacar?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>Ilimitado.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>5.Quantas vezes posso sacar por dia?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>5 vezes/dia.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>6.Por que n\u00e3o consigo sacar fundos usando minha conta de saque?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>A mesma conta de saque s\u00f3 pode ser vinculada a duas contas do aplicativo, no m\u00e1ximo. N\u00e3o compartilhe a conta com outras pessoas.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>7.Posso usar VPN?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>O uso de VPN \u00e9 proibido, por favor, n\u00e3o a utilize.</font><br>"

    .line 11
    .line 12
    iput-object p1, p0, Lw3/j;->d:Ljava/lang/String;

    .line 13
    .line 14
    const-string p1, "\n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>1.Bagaimana cara menarik uang tunai?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>Ada hadiah uang tunai untuk setiap level yang Anda lalui. Semakin banyak level yang Anda lalui, semakin banyak hadiah yang Anda dapatkan. Anda dapat menarik uang tunai saat Anda memenuhi persyaratan.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>2.Berapa lama waktu yang dibutuhkan untuk menarik uang?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>Umumnya, dana akan dikreditkan ke akun Anda dalam beberapa menit. Saat jumlah penarikan atau jumlahnya melebihi batas tertentu, sistem akan meninjaunya, tetapi juga akan dikreditkan ke akun Anda dalam waktu 24 jam, jangan khawatir.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>3.Mengapa penarikan saya gagal?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>Jika penarikan gagal, sistem akan memberikan umpan balik tentang alasan kegagalan (dalam bahasa Inggris). Harap ubah sesuai dengan petunjuk. Jika penarikan gagal, sistem akan mengembalikan jumlah penarikan. Anda dapat mengubah informasi penarikan dan memulai kembali penarikan. Pastikan informasi yang Anda isi sudah benar. Kami tidak bertanggung jawab atas kegagalan penarikan yang disebabkan oleh informasi yang salah.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>4.Berapa kali saya dapat menarik uang?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>Tidak terbatas.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>5.Berapa kali saya dapat menarik uang dalam sehari?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>5 kali/hari</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>6.Mengapa saya tidak dapat menarik dana menggunakan akun penarikan saya?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>Akun penarikan yang sama hanya dapat dikaitkan dengan maksimal dua akun aplikasi. Mohon jangan bagikan akun dengan orang lain.</font><br>\n<br>        \n<font color=\'#CD582F\'>7.Dapatkah saya menggunakan VPN?</font><br>\n<font color=\'#325D00\'>Penggunaan VPN dilarang, mohon jangan menggunakannya.</font><br>"

